#MEM id=delivery-status source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/skills/marketplace/delivery-status/SKILL.md savings=8%
M||tx|---
M||name|ring:delivery-status
M||desc|\|
M||tx|Delivery status tracking and progress reporting. Analyzes repository against
M||tx|delivery roadmap to calculate actual vs planned progress, identify delays,
M||tx|and provide in on velocity and risk tn.
M||tx|---
M|When|- De|pre-dv-delivery-planning)
M|When|it|Need to check progress against plan
M|When|it|Stakeholders requesting status up
M|When|it|Regular checkpoint (weekly/sprint end)
M|Skip|- No|pre-dv-delivery-planning
M|Skip|it|Planning phase only → execute tasks first
M|Skip|it|No repository activity → nothing to al
M|Sequ|**Ru|** ring:pre-dv-delivery-planning, ring:dv-cycle
M|Sequ|tx|Every status rp must be grounded in repository evidence, not estimates or verbal updates. Status answers WHAT is actually done vs what was planned.
M|Mand|tx|\| Phase \| Activities \|
M|Mand|tx|\|-------\|------------\|
M|Mand|tx|\| **1. Input Gathering** \| Load delivery-roadmap.md (required), tasks.md (required), subtasks.md (optional), current date \|
M|Mand|tx|\| **2. Repository Scan** \| Scan ALL branches, commits, PRs, releases; bd activity timeline; identify task-related work \|
M|Mand|tx|\| **3. Task Matching** \| Pattern matching (branches, commits, PRs) + semantic al (code cn vs scope) via specialized ag \|
M|Mand|| **|al scope items found vs expected; calculate % done; determine status \|
M|Mand|tx|\| **5. Variance al** \| Compare planned vs actual dates; identify delays/early completions; calculate ct path impact \|
M|Mand|tx|\| **6. in Extraction** \| Velocity tn, bug rate, rv time, code patterns, risk indicators \|
M|Mand|tx|\| **7. rp Generation** \| Save to `doc/pre-dv/{feature}/delivery-status-{date}.md`; include evidence links \|
M|Mand|**Q1|Repository** — Which org/repo to al? (format: org/repo)
M|Mand|**Q2|Roadmap Source** — Options: File path (local), GitHub URL (raw), Document link, Paste cn
M|Mand|**Q3|Tasks File** — Same options as Q2 (REQUIRED — not optional)
M|Mand|**Q4|Subtasks File** — Yes (w/ source options) or No (al at task level only)
M|Mand|**Q5|al Date** — Today (auto-detect) or Custom date (accepts DD/MM/YYYY or YYYY-MM-DD)
M|Repo|tx|```bash
M|Scan|tx|git fetch --all && git branch -a
M|Scan|git |"%H\|%an\|%ae\|%ad\|%s" --date=iso
M|Find|tx|git branch -a \| grep -iE "T-[0-9]+\|task\|feature\|fix"
M|Get |tx|gh pr list --state all --limit 100 --json number,title,state,mergedAt,headRefName
M|Find|tx|git log --all --name-only --format="%H\|%ad\|%s" --date=iso \| grep -v "^$"
M|Find|tx|```
M|Task|1. *|** Search branch names, PR titles, commit messages for T-XXX patterns
M|Task|2. *|** Dispatch specialized ag per task tp to al actual code changes vs task scope
M|Task|3. *|** Count scope items found (endpoints, tests, migrations) vs expected
M|Task|tx|\| Signal \| Weight \|
M|Task|tx|\|--------\|--------\|
M|Task|tx|\| PR merged to main \| hi (but validate scope completion) \|
M|Task|tx|\| Feature branch active \| md \|
M|Task|tx|\| Commits w/ task reference \| md \|
M|Task|tx|\| Code changes matching scope \| hi \|
M|Task|tx|\| tst files for task scope \| hi \|
M|Stat|tx|\| Status \| Criteria \|
M|Stat|tx|\|--------\|----------\|
M|Stat|tx|\| ✅ Complete \| All scope items found; tests present; merged to main \|
M|Stat|tx|\| 🔄 In Progress \| Active branch; partial scope found; open PR \|
M|Stat|tx|\| ⏸️ Not Started \| No branch, no commits matching this task \|
M|Stat|tx|\| ⚠️ At Risk \| Started but behind schedule per ct path \|
M|Stat|tx|\| ❌ blk \| No progress for >3 days on ct path task \|
M|Repo|tx|```markdown
M|Exec|- Ov|🟢 On Track \| 🟡 At Risk \| 🔴 Behind
M|Exec|- Pl|{date}
M|Exec|- Re|{date} (if different)
M|Task|tx|\| Task \| Status \| % Done \| Planned End \| Actual/fc \| Variance \| Evidence \|
M|Task|tx|\|------\|--------\|--------\|-------------\|-----------------\|----------\|----------\|
M|Task|tx|\| T-001 \| ✅ Complete \| 100% \| 2026-03-10 \| 2026-03-09 \| +1 day early \| [PR #42] \|
M|Task|tx|\| T-002 \| 🔄 In Progress \| 65% \| 2026-03-20 \| 2026-03-22 \| -2 days late \| [branch] \|
M|Peri|- Sp|✅ Done (2 complete, 1 partial)
M|Peri|- Sp|🔄 In Progress
M|in|- Ve|X tasks/sprint (planned Y)
M|in|- Av|X days
M|in|- Bu|X bugs per task
M|Risk|it|[T-002 is on ct path, currently -2 days]
M|Reco|it|[Action items w/ owners and dates]
M|Reco|tx|```
M|Evid|Ever|
M|Evid|it|PR URL (merged)
M|Evid|it|Commit hash w/ message
M|Evid|it|File path showing relevant changes
M|Evid|it|tst file path confirming coverage
M|Evid|tx|Never rp completion w/o evidence links.